description: You're currently in the control center of your spacecraft good ole Betsy. Try taking off!
You've landed on planet Silverton. There's not alot of silver but there's a ton of trouble!
You've landed on planet Nuthinmuch. Not much 'round these parts best we head back to the ship.
You've landed on the beatiful planet of Get Along Lil Doggy. You're not too sure what a doggy is but that doesn't keep you from exploring.
You've landed on planet Deadman. Not too sure how it got it's name but let's not stay and find out!
You managed to wander up here to your bedroom. Now is no time to sleep partner! There's evil afoot!
Now you're in your bathroom. Could you kindly hurry up and take off soon?
You entered the saloon and spot the Martian passed out at the bar from his 10th shot of whiskey! Way to go space cowboy!
You've entered the stables and no martian in sight but you see some horses. Oh the pioneers use to ride these babies for miles!
